reviewText: Like fishing? Like comedy? Then you can't go wrong with T.K. & Mike Mike & T.K. (You'll get it when you watch it). They'll have you in stitches!
If you love fishing and comedy this is a must have!!!

Not much new, but has some high points of humor. Their Southern Redneck approach to things is always fun and you have to know something about that part of the world to appreciate it. So sad we lost one at such a young age.
Probably the best of the series in my opinion. Good slapstick humor spread throughout though script writing could have been better for this one and the others in the series. Still, it's fun.
